name: DepressedThoughts
tweet:
I wish people would quit believing in me.

It just makes the list of people I will disappoint that much longer.

Not to mention the list of people I have already disappointed.

Just let me disappoint myself.

#depression #depressed #depressedthoughts

name: DepressedThoughts
tweet:
I am afraid of death.

I don't want to die.

Yet this still does not motivate me to do things I enjoy.

Die happy, or die sad.

Either way, you die so what's the point?

#depression #depressed #depressedthoughts

tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #MajorDepressiveDisorder (#MDD) happens when a person has at least two weeks of #depressed mood.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood is often one of the early symptoms of hypothyroidism (reduced activity of the thyroid gland).

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood can be caused by infectious diseases, nutritional deficiencies, neurological conditions, and physiological problems.

tweet: Certain medications are known to cause #depressed mood in a significant number of patients.

tweet: #Depressed people may have problems concentrating, remembering details or making decisions, and may contemplate, attempt or commit suicide.

tweet: Older #depressed people may have cognitive symptoms of recent onset, such as #forgetfulness, and a more noticeable slowing of movements.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #MajorDepressiveDisorder (#MDD) happens when a person has at least two weeks of #depressed mood.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood is often one of the early symptoms of hypothyroidism (reduced activity of the thyroid gland).

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood can be caused by infectious diseases, nutritional deficiencies, neurological conditions, and physiological problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Certain medications are known to cause #depressed mood in a significant number of patients.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed people may have problems concentrating, remembering details or making decisions, and may contemplate, attempt or commit suicide.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Older #depressed people may have cognitive symptoms of recent onset, such as #forgetfulness, and a more noticeable slowing of movements.

Die happy, or die sad.

Either way, you die so what's the point?

#depression #depressed #depressedthoughts

name: Mohamed Hamdy 🇪🇬
tweet:
If you think you're #depressed, please do the following:

1. DO NOT diagnose yourself based on some social media posts, sometimes you're just sad.
2. Seek help from a professional (psychiatrist or a certified therapist).

#Depression is a serious illness. Don't take it lightly.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #MajorDepressiveDisorder (#MDD) happens when a person has at least two weeks of #depressed mood.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood is often one of the early symptoms of hypothyroidism (reduced activity of the thyroid gland).

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood can be caused by infectious diseases, nutritional deficiencies, neurological conditions, and physiological problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Certain medications are known to cause #depressed mood in a significant number of patients.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed people may have problems concentrating, remembering details or making decisions, and may contemplate, attempt or commit suicide.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Older #depressed people may have cognitive symptoms of recent onset, such as #forgetfulness, and a more noticeable slowing of movements.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweeting about r self enlightenment living life #bipolar #depressed #anxious how u r ur first biggest support Others r on their own journey in life too. We can’t be there 4 them. We do have clarity enough to learn and adjust not just survive. Hospitalized is different

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweets saying today is another day I’m #depressed so I’m taking care of myself. Chemicals make me depressed I can’t fix that but will not add to it. I will focus on me resisting the thought I’m the only person lonely abandoned tired ashamed. All humans feel

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do we know/like our #bipolar selves. Why do we fight to feel NORMAL who the hell is actually normal you know. We are messed up just like every other human we know. Why do we degrade ourselves 4 being #depressed while others don’t degrade themselves for being ignorant #abusive etc

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: #bipolardisorder why do we insist on taking people on tours of our life/day. “See I’m #depressed I’m #anxious; don’t YOU understand?” Why do THEY need to understand? What JOB are you assigning them??

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: We know why we do lie about our #Bipolar day to day state. How do you tell people over and over that today you are #depressed or #manic again? It feels like they may be keeping count and you hit your limit long ago.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: When your nighttime dream of your ex is so beautiful that when you are awake the next day you're #depressed it's not real. #Dream betrayal

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: More #suicides occur on #Mondays. Returning to the same grind on Monday may make #depressed or #MentallIll people believe there is no change everything remains the same as the week starts all over again hopelessness for a better tomorrow

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Actually having people around you during Christmas seems to make #depressed or #MentallyIll people postpone their plans for suicide to at least January 1st if they do it at all then. So checking up on people during holidays may help save a life.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It is so wrong to think beautiful sexy people don't get #depressed. Look at the pictures of those saying they're ready to quit

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Remember #bipolar people are more likely to seek help while #depressed and not while #manic. Most do not perceive that there is a problem because emotions/moods are elevated and they tend to blame outside forces for their discomfort if any is perceived.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It was easy for me to identify my #manic state but not my #depressed state. After my last episode I realized my depressed state was anger/rage. I only thought of the depressive state as that I can't do anything mode. And I was actually a little violent which scared me and family

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I just to have to wait it out. Sleeping pills don't even help (prescribed) I actually can break down and cry when it happens. No one understands how horrible it is to not be able to sleep. I get angry and #Depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do not let the comments of people who do not understand #MentalHealthDisorders Read Learn Understand your #bipolar disorder so these comments can bounce off of you. You do not pick days to be bipolar #depressed #anxious #mybipolarstory pic.twitter.com/FOLHwqr6T5

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: @LeeMartin113 @mentalhealthuk people don't realize there are a range of emotions besides #manic or #depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: No #Santa #Clause I'm #Depressed ok I'm #naughty too pic.twitter.com/ua21ErsPY3

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Just like people get #depressed during the #holidays people get overly happy #Christmas including Santa Clause pic.twitter.com/bDe6T1FVDD

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I feel the same. I'm not sure if I know who I really am. I think I am more of my #manic self than my #depressed self. Who knows? #mybipolarstory

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: The #holidays are here. hate #Thanksgiving #Christmas #Easter 4th of July. It is forced social activity I have #socialanxiety After each holiday I am left for a week either #manic or #depressed I never know which one it will be. I like #halloween though I'm good at wearing masks pic.twitter.com/iC3xKujLdp

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: People believe being #bipolar means you are either #manic or #depressed happy or #sad I wish it was that simple. #bipolardisorder has a middle where you are not crying or smiling #mybipolarstory #mentalhealth pic.twitter.com/cpBsqxMHbK

tweet: Paul wrote, “God, who comforts the #depressed, comforted us by the coming of Titus” (2 Corinthians 7:6), certainly knew seasons of darkness and despair. . name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #MajorDepressiveDisorder (#MDD) happens when a person has at least two weeks of #depressed mood.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood is often one of the early symptoms of hypothyroidism (reduced activity of the thyroid gland).

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood can be caused by infectious diseases, nutritional deficiencies, neurological conditions, and physiological problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Certain medications are known to cause #depressed mood in a significant number of patients.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed people may have problems concentrating, remembering details or making decisions, and may contemplate, attempt or commit suicide.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Older #depressed people may have cognitive symptoms of recent onset, such as #forgetfulness, and a more noticeable slowing of movements.

name: Dan Bough 💻☁️🍺⚽️⛩⚙️
tweet: I overheard someone telling a story today where a guy told his (literally) #depressed brother that “you need to pull yourself together for your kids!”  I get it, we want to believe that someone going through depression can just snap themselves out of it.

tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: My #NewYearsResolution (after this tweet) is to no longer tag celebrities on here. @HamillHimself is still my favorite, but I'm not as cool as his popular fans, so I will go back to my corner where I am invisible. Hopefully my real dream will not leave me #depressed like in 2019!

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Ever log onto #twitter and get a bit #depressed because you aren't part of the "crowd" a tweet is referring to? At least I've found good people on #YouTube who don't make me feel like a complete loser like I have on #twitch lately. (Singled out for not being #affiliate hurts)

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Was hoping to #stream on #twitch today, but extremely #depressed now and I feel like raising the white flag. Gonna make some #YouTube videos instead since at least that is starting to grow and receive some encouragement. https://www.youtube.com/c/MysticPoet82

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Oof, that #depressed feeling you get when you know you're not far away from having to go to bed because work is the next day. I seriously wish I could just retire now so I could have the proper amount of time to work on my #dreamjob 😭

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Super #depressed tonight. Just one of those times I wish I wasn't alive anymore.  pic.twitter.com/Kc4X8zkcFc

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: It's really sad how even so called "family" will jump at the opportunity to blame you for everything when you did nothing wrong. Proof that they truly wouldn't give 2 shits if something happened and you died. #depressed #depression

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet:
Car broke down again and I was very close to jumping out in front of a truck on the highway to end it all. Need some cheering up if you can @HamillHimself 
and don't anyone dare respond with suicide hotline messages or I will block you. #SaturdayMorning #depressed

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Was going to #stream but last time it got me pretty #depressed. I'm pretty sure I will be able to Saturday evening though. Only if you are willing to watch, which one should I play?  pic.twitter.com/f1AVYVd9op

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Not a good start to my week, I hurt someone's feelings without meaning to, and it just shows I'm a worthless piece of shit. If happiness and a dream come true was meant for anyone, it's obvious now that it's not me. #depressed

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: My nerves are so shot that I feel like I could puke at any moment. #depressed

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Mentally I feel like I just got slammed up against a brick wall and was left in a pained heap on the ground while everyone just walked by without even a glance. It's all I can do right now to maintain a tear free composure. #depressed

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: You know it's bad when you're too #depressed to do what actually makes you happy. Dunno when the next #Stream will be, still feeling down and considering just giving up.

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: This week has been horribly draining of my energy to #Stream. At this point I'm just super #depressed from being so tired. I wish I just knew if better things were around the corner for me on #twitch or if I should just give up on that and all my current #DREAMS.

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Sometimes I hate having such strong levels of sensitivity to make me 😭, when just a few minutes before I was 😂. I feel so #worthless and that there's no way I can possibly make a difference in the lives of others like I dream of doing. #depression #depressed #ThursdayThoughts

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Not feeling myself this week at all, and the only thing that has made me #happy is streaming. Not only that, but having such amazing friends who stop by to hang out. I don't fully know why I'm #depressed but I do need closure on something and I may never receive it.

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet:
Feeling a bit down tonight. I wish things would look up instead of me going to bed in tears. I have a sinking feeling my birthday is going to be bad, and I'm not looking forward to that. 
#Depression #depressed  pic.twitter.com/V9kLfW2CXr

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: This day is complete hell, and it's only started. #ThursdayThoughts #depression #depressed

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: It's one of those days. I was drained physically from work & then mentally after. I really wish things would get better, but I'm afraid that if I keep my hopes up too high & they do start looking up, they'll just crash & burn, like every time before. #depressed #mentalhealth

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: I know no one with any influence will see this or even care, but I've come to the realization that working retail at the same place for 14 years and watching things go constantly downhill is really making me want to commit suicide. #suicide #depression #depressed #TuesdayThoughts

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Ever have one of those moments where you feel like you just don't belong anywhere and all you want is a friend who understands and whose shoulder you could cry on, but you're just completely alone to cry yourself to sleep? #depressed #depression #MentalHealth #loneliness

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet:
It was going okay,  then I lost another sub. When you're a small #youtuber suffering #depression  it's so hard to keep from crying and wanting to just give up completely on everything. Getting to 200 seems so far away now that I've about lost hope. #depressed
#SundayMorning

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: I would rather hear, "You can do it!" Than "It's a lot of hard work" #SundayMorning #depression #depressed #mentalillness  Remember, it's how you say it that's important, so choose your words wisely.

name: 🦄Mystic🐲
tweet: Ever stop & think that you work so hard for what feels like nothing except the means to just barely get by in life? It's obvious that those who work the hardest are the least appreciated and most taken advantage of. Would love to see that change. #SaturdayNight #depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweeting about r self enlightenment living life #bipolar #depressed #anxious how u r ur first biggest support Others r on their own journey in life too. We can’t be there 4 them. We do have clarity enough to learn and adjust not just survive. Hospitalized is different

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweets saying today is another day I’m #depressed so I’m taking care of myself. Chemicals make me depressed I can’t fix that but will not add to it. I will focus on me resisting the thought I’m the only person lonely abandoned tired ashamed. All humans feel

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do we know/like our #bipolar selves. Why do we fight to feel NORMAL who the hell is actually normal you know. We are messed up just like every other human we know. Why do we degrade ourselves 4 being #depressed while others don’t degrade themselves for being ignorant #abusive etc

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: #bipolardisorder why do we insist on taking people on tours of our life/day. “See I’m #depressed I’m #anxious; don’t YOU understand?” Why do THEY need to understand? What JOB are you assigning them??

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: We know why we do lie about our #Bipolar day to day state. How do you tell people over and over that today you are #depressed or #manic again? It feels like they may be keeping count and you hit your limit long ago.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: When your nighttime dream of your ex is so beautiful that when you are awake the next day you're #depressed it's not real. #Dream betrayal

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: More #suicides occur on #Mondays. Returning to the same grind on Monday may make #depressed or #MentallIll people believe there is no change everything remains the same as the week starts all over again hopelessness for a better tomorrow

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Actually having people around you during Christmas seems to make #depressed or #MentallyIll people postpone their plans for suicide to at least January 1st if they do it at all then. So checking up on people during holidays may help save a life.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It is so wrong to think beautiful sexy people don't get #depressed. Look at the pictures of those saying they're ready to quit

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Remember #bipolar people are more likely to seek help while #depressed and not while #manic. Most do not perceive that there is a problem because emotions/moods are elevated and they tend to blame outside forces for their discomfort if any is perceived.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: #PeteDavidson soul looks #depressed and tired. Hope family/friends gets him to admit himself sounds/looks like it's time. I don't want to see another public #celebrity breakdown. #MentalHealth needs supportive family/friends to know when to say when #mybipolarstory

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It was easy for me to identify my #manic state but not my #depressed state. After my last episode I realized my depressed state was anger/rage. I only thought of the depressive state as that I can't do anything mode. And I was actually a little violent which scared me and family

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I just to have to wait it out. Sleeping pills don't even help (prescribed) I actually can break down and cry when it happens. No one understands how horrible it is to not be able to sleep. I get angry and #Depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do not let the comments of people who do not understand #MentalHealthDisorders Read Learn Understand your #bipolar disorder so these comments can bounce off of you. You do not pick days to be bipolar #depressed #anxious #mybipolarstory pic.twitter.com/FOLHwqr6T5

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: @LeeMartin113 @mentalhealthuk people don't realize there are a range of emotions besides #manic or #depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: No #Santa #Clause I'm #Depressed ok I'm #naughty too pic.twitter.com/ua21ErsPY3

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Just like people get #depressed during the #holidays people get overly happy #Christmas including Santa Clause pic.twitter.com/bDe6T1FVDD

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I feel the same. I'm not sure if I know who I really am. I think I am more of my #manic self than my #depressed self. Who knows? #mybipolarstory

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: The #holidays are here. hate #Thanksgiving #Christmas #Easter 4th of July. It is forced social activity I have #socialanxiety After each holiday I am left for a week either #manic or #depressed I never know which one it will be. I like #halloween though I'm good at wearing masks pic.twitter.com/iC3xKujLdp

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: People believe being #bipolar means you are either #manic or #depressed happy or #sad I wish it was that simple. #bipolardisorder has a middle where you are not crying or smiling #mybipolarstory #mentalhealth pic.twitter.com/cpBsqxMHbK

name: AnnieT
tweet: The days between Christmas and New Year are the toughest for some. When one day at a time feels impossible, do Life in 15min chunks. Complete one 15min chunk before thinking about the next.  It will get easier. Eventually a whole day will feel perfectly doable. #sad #depressed  pic.twitter.com/XjFQnCcCZV

tweet: Do yourself a favour when you are feeling #depressed, #sad and low. Stop what ever you are doing. Pull out your notes on your phone and ask yourself why do you feel that way and what actions you can do right now to change. Then take those actions immediately

tweet: #HarshFacts some people that are #depressed lie when they say they are asked how are you? Because they don't want to hear things that don't resonate with ideally what they want

name: V1 Coaching Ltd
tweet: #HarshFacts #Depression is personal. No one can really tell you why you're #depressed. The best anyone can do for you is help ease out of this state of mind. And not judge you for what has been going on through your mind and in your life.

name: V1 Coaching Ltd
tweet: #MondayMotivation when you are feeling #depressed and you take a walk outside for 15-30 mins and now you're back and your head is clear and you are back to thinking rational thoughts.

name: V1 Coaching Ltd
tweet: There is no need to fall back into the #sunkenplace. Don't you dare go back to being and feeling #depressed. Use that energy to continue using the tools available to you to achieve your desired result. Doing nothing will only make matters worse. Doing something now = happiness

tweet: A #Depressed person may report multiple physical symptoms such as fatigue, headaches, or digestive problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Insomnia is common among the #Depressed. In the typical pattern, a person wakes very early and cannot get back to sleep.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: A #MajorDepressiveDisorder (#MDD) happens when a person has at least two weeks of #depressed mood.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood is often one of the early symptoms of hypothyroidism (reduced activity of the thyroid gland).

name: Lower Depression
tweet: #Depressed mood can be caused by infectious diseases, nutritional deficiencies, neurological conditions, and physiological problems.

name: Lower Depression
tweet: Certain medications are known to cause #depressed mood in a significant number of patients.

tweet: #Depressed people may have problems concentrating, remembering details or making decisions, and may contemplate, attempt or commit suicide.

tweet: Older #depressed people may have cognitive symptoms of recent onset, such as #forgetfulness, and a more noticeable slowing of movements.

tweet:
To someone #depressed
Stop feeling sorry for yourself.
It's all in your head.
You don't look sick.
Did you take your meds.
You're not trusting in God.
People have it worse.
You're lazy.
You're not trying hard enough.
Smile, be positive.
You need a hobby.
#ThingsYouJustShouldntSay

tweet:

Because since, I've been truly #depressed #bpd

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet: There are up's a down's in my life and this is defiantly a down. Having to cut off a family member, who doesn't respect my #sobriety. I just can't imagine having to lose another person who I've gotten so close to, but I have to do what's right for me. Very #depressed about this.

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet:
It makes me so #depressed knowing that I missed my career calling and it's to late to go back and re-do my college, that once I thought I wanted to pursue.

I should have been a veterinarian. Honestly, my folks are right. I just never realized it. Until later.

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet:
I don't want to acknowledge my birthday but I don't get that choice.. 

Our weather can get really bad on my birthday which always disrupts my plans & is a reason I don't make plans. 

This year, I don't think I'll be up to do much. #depressed 

Things are bad.

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet: And the worst thing about it is that I'm only on 1/2 of my dose of Effexor, which means this is not going to go away, it may lessen or I may be burdened with it until this is over. It's all coming back again once i stop taking this 1/2 dose tapering. It makes me #depressed.

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet: What am I thinking, I'm so far out of my comfort zone I shake when I post the link to helping me build a positive coping skills  http://a.co/1ikcQ9l  . I haven't asked for help before now. But I need to, they say, when #depressed & #hopeless. I'm kind of down in dark again.

name: ♡ ᖴᖇᑌITᒪOOᑭ ♡
tweet: Getting pretty #depressed honestly, going back down that route where in the past has led to hospitalizations, bad thoughts. I feel like a #failure, atm. I had such high hopes for myself today, this Monday, I realized too high of hopes to change my life in a day. Still sad though.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: What do I expect of myself for the month of #June? I expect to start telling myself that "I can" instead of "I can't". It's going to be very hard convincing a very #depressed mind that I can do more then rot til death. I expect to start working out my #depression as well.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: I'm feeling so #depressed right now I cannot wait to go home and hatch a new #Tamagotchi egg. Raising a new Tama will help my endless sadness.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: I often struggle with self patience cause I never asked to be #depressed although #life situations and #sexuality issues among #selfhatred was enough to bring me in that boat for years. But this sailor wants to find a new boat but I can't find it cause #depression is all I know.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: Feeling even more severely #depressed today because in addition to the usual things I'm depressed about I'm starting to see that me being #gay will always keep me from having a friend. It's the most lonely experience I've ever had and don't want to be gay anymore.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: It took me over a decade to accept my #homosexuality and that it can never be changed. But even with that knowledge I'm getting very depressed because #sexuality is completly wasted on me as an #introvert #depressed #socialanxiety sufferer. I'm gay for no reason it seems.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: The second half of today's vlog continuing to detail my struggles of being #Depressed while living in an #Apartment that is nothing more but an experience of distress.  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SbAwtvWGros … #MentalHealth #MentalIllness #Suicide #MaleDepression

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: Going to finally force myself out on a #Depression walk to say to myself I don't want to be #Depressed anymore. With the climate slightly warmer and the snow melted (at least from the sidewalks) it's becoming easier to fulfill. Again my depression walk requires 7,000 steps!

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: I'm finding that more and more I'm blaming myself for having #Depression because of my past failures that really has no relation to #MentalHealth outside of it being affected by such. If I wasn't #Depressed I wouldn't feel like such a loser.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: Feeling completely #Invisible to the world. Usually when I get this bad I lose my reasons for wanting to continue to fight my #MentalIllness. Sometimes I wonder if I truly do deserve to be #Depressed.

name: Khristiaan Parker
tweet: I hope so cause it never feels like that with me. #Outsider #Lonely #Depressed #SocialAnxiety #Suicidal

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweeting about r self enlightenment living life #bipolar #depressed #anxious how u r ur first biggest support Others r on their own journey in life too. We can’t be there 4 them. We do have clarity enough to learn and adjust not just survive. Hospitalized is different

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Let’s start tweets saying today is another day I’m #depressed so I’m taking care of myself. Chemicals make me depressed I can’t fix that but will not add to it. I will focus on me resisting the thought I’m the only person lonely abandoned tired ashamed. All humans feel

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do we know/like our #bipolar selves. Why do we fight to feel NORMAL who the hell is actually normal you know. We are messed up just like every other human we know. Why do we degrade ourselves 4 being #depressed while others don’t degrade themselves for being ignorant #abusive etc

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: #bipolardisorder why do we insist on taking people on tours of our life/day. “See I’m #depressed I’m #anxious; don’t YOU understand?” Why do THEY need to understand? What JOB are you assigning them??

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: We know why we do lie about our #Bipolar day to day state. How do you tell people over and over that today you are #depressed or #manic again? It feels like they may be keeping count and you hit your limit long ago.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: When your nighttime dream of your ex is so beautiful that when you are awake the next day you're #depressed it's not real. #Dream betrayal

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: More #suicides occur on #Mondays. Returning to the same grind on Monday may make #depressed or #MentallIll people believe there is no change everything remains the same as the week starts all over again hopelessness for a better tomorrow

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Actually having people around you during Christmas seems to make #depressed or #MentallyIll people postpone their plans for suicide to at least January 1st if they do it at all then. So checking up on people during holidays may help save a life.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It is so wrong to think beautiful sexy people don't get #depressed. Look at the pictures of those saying they're ready to quit

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Remember #bipolar people are more likely to seek help while #depressed and not while #manic. Most do not perceive that there is a problem because emotions/moods are elevated and they tend to blame outside forces for their discomfort if any is perceived.

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: #PeteDavidson soul looks #depressed and tired. Hope family/friends gets him to admit himself sounds/looks like it's time. I don't want to see another public #celebrity breakdown. #MentalHealth needs supportive family/friends to know when to say when #mybipolarstory

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: It was easy for me to identify my #manic state but not my #depressed state. After my last episode I realized my depressed state was anger/rage. I only thought of the depressive state as that I can't do anything mode. And I was actually a little violent which scared me and family

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I just to have to wait it out. Sleeping pills don't even help (prescribed) I actually can break down and cry when it happens. No one understands how horrible it is to not be able to sleep. I get angry and #Depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Do not let the comments of people who do not understand #MentalHealthDisorders Read Learn Understand your #bipolar disorder so these comments can bounce off of you. You do not pick days to be bipolar #depressed #anxious #mybipolarstory pic.twitter.com/FOLHwqr6T5

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: @LeeMartin113 @mentalhealthuk people don't realize there are a range of emotions besides #manic or #depressed

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: No #Santa #Clause I'm #Depressed ok I'm #naughty too pic.twitter.com/ua21ErsPY3

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: Just like people get #depressed during the #holidays people get overly happy #Christmas including Santa Clause pic.twitter.com/bDe6T1FVDD

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: I feel the same. I'm not sure if I know who I really am. I think I am more of my #manic self than my #depressed self. Who knows? #mybipolarstory

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: The #holidays are here. hate #Thanksgiving #Christmas #Easter 4th of July. It is forced social activity I have #socialanxiety After each holiday I am left for a week either #manic or #depressed I never know which one it will be. I like #halloween though I'm good at wearing masks pic.twitter.com/iC3xKujLdp

name: My Bipolar Story
tweet: People believe being #bipolar means you are either #manic or #depressed happy or #sad I wish it was that simple. #bipolardisorder has a middle where you are not crying or smiling #mybipolarstory #mentalhealth pic.twitter.com/cpBsqxMHbK

I feel like I've shared this recently. But, this song has helped me get through some dark times for many years. When I'm feeling dangerously #depressed & when this song comes up on my mix, I feel a sense of hope again. #Coldplay #IveGotToGetOutOfThisHole
 https://youtu.be/LGt8O7F-Qbc

I hate waking up #depressed or crying as soon as my eyes open to a dark room, alone. It's like a headache and it stays with you for the rest of the day.
